<HEADLINE>
<P>
CATHOLIC JUSTICES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In view of the tremendous pressure being applied by the Catholic Church on all 
abortion related issues, it seems that the five Catholic members of the Supreme 
Court should recuse themselves on all such decisions to avoid even the 
appearance of conflict. Why is there nodiscussion of this? 
</P>
<P>
MARGARET ROSS 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
