industries try to zero in on their targets.' ; Photo, Charles D. Peebler Jr.: 
'We will all need a deeper understanding of what makes people tick.' ; Photo, 
Norman W. Brown: 'Environment and health considerations have started to become 
important . . . ' ; Photo, Phillip B. Dusenberry: 'No one can predict what 
advertising will be like in the 1990s.' 
</P>
