EL CAJON FIRM IN CONTRACT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
R. M. Microsystems Inc. in El Cajon won a $4.1-million contract from the Navy 
for design and analysis related to EHF systems network and control. 
</P>
