<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSWATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Dana Parsons 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NATURAL DISASTER: The gusty winds buffeting Orange County (A1) may seem 
threatening, but they're lightweights compared to the county's No. 1 natural 
enemy of the last few years: winter's cold. . . . Last winter, the county 
sustained more than $30 million in crop damage, mostly the result of cold 
weather. Dana Parsons 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
